net.marfgamer.jraknet.identifier

Class Identifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.marfgamer.jraknet.identifier.Identifier
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MinecraftIdentifier

    public class Identifier
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an identifier sent from a server on the local network, any class extending this only has to override the build() method in order to have their identifier be dynamic.
    Author:
    Whirvis "MarfGamer" Ardenaur
